These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, white, emerald, blood-red
City: hamburg, rome, edinburgh, paris
4 different games are played: snooker, poker, chess, go
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, january, october, july
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, hamster, mouse
House: tower, palace, craftsman, futuristic
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, begonia, daisy, balloon-flower
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person playing go##1
 2. the person playing poker is the owner of the cat##1
 3. the person who likes emerald is not the person who growsbegonia##6
 4. the person who growsdaisy is not the person who likes white##6
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the craftsman house##5
 6. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
 7. the person who growsballoon-flower is not the palace house##6
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 9. the person traveling to edinburgh is not the person who likes blood-red##6
10. the person traveling to paris is the person who growsbegonia##1
11. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person who growsrose##1
12. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
13. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the futuristic house##1
14. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
15. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
16. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere between the person who growsbegonia and the person who growsballoon-flower##7
17. the futuristic house is not the person who's birthday is in august##6
18. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
19. the palace house is somewhere between the person traveling to hamburg and the tower house##7
20. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person who likes blood-red##6
21. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Color          | orange      | blood-red   | white     | emerald |
| City           | paris | rome   | hamburg    | edinburgh     |
| Game   | go       | chess | snooker   | poker   |
| Birthday   | october      | july     | august | january    |
| Pet           | chinchilla   | mouse       | hamster  | cat       |
| House         | tower     | palace     | craftsman | futuristic   |
| Flower     | begonia          | daisy      | balloon-flower     | rose      |

